name: Coffee Session
description:
The elements that I can't live without are Coffee, Cigarettes, and Talk.

I talk a lot. Like, a lot. These 3 have always been my day-to-day survival kit to this day. But lately, I'm kinda sad because my friends who always accompany me to living this coffee-and-talk started to get hard to reach one-by-one.

Some of them are married, have a new family, but some are just busy with their life. I don't know if i can keep living this kinda life or not, but right now, those are still my main method to living this harden life day by day.
